<h2 id="접근하기">접근하기</h2>

<p>주어진 수를 3진수으로 변환 후 뒤집는다. 그리고 다시 10진수로 변환 후 반환한다.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="내-코드">내 코드</h2>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">function</span> <span class="nx">solution</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">n</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">base3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">n</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">toString</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">);</span>
  <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">toArr</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">base3</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">''</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">reverse</span><span class="p">();</span>
  <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">toStr</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">toArr</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">''</span><span class="p">);</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nb">parseInt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">toStr</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
